import React from "react";
import { Document, Page, View, Image, Text } from "react-pdf/renderer";

const Pdf = ({ showModal, id, facturas }) => {
  const arrayEditado = facturas.filter((itemid) => itemid.id === id);
  console.log(arrayEditado);
  return (
    <>
      {showModal && id ? (
        <Document>
          <Page size="A4">
            <View className="justify-center items-center flex overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto fixed inset-0 z-50 outline-none focus:outline-none">
              <View className="relative w-auto my-6 mx-auto max-w-3xl">
                {/*content*/}
                <View className="border-0 rounded-lg shadow-lg relative flex flex-col w-full bg-white outline-none focus:outline-none">
                  {/*header*/}
                  <View className="flex  justify-between p-5 border-b border-solid border-slate-200 rounded-t items-center flex-col ">
                    <View className="text-3xl font-semibold">
                      FACTURA <Text className="text-redO">#{id}</Text>{" "}
                    </View>
                    <View
                      src="https://i.imgur.com/iMYhMud.png"
                      alt="imagen Usuario"
                      className="w-40 max-auto ml-5"
                    />
                    <View className="block">
                      <Text>Wilberth Mora Piedra</Text>
                      <View className="flex flex-row">
                        <Image
                          src="http://assets.stickpng.com/thumbs/5a4525cd546ddca7e1fcbc84.png"
                          alt="imagen ubi"
                          className="w-5 max-auto ml-1"
                        />
                        <Text>2472/2811 - 8865/6842</Text>
                      </View>
                      <View className="flex flex-row">
                        <Image
                          src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/0/619.png"
                          alt="imagen ubi"
                          className="w-5 max-auto ml-1"
                        />
                        <Text>venecia, San Carlos</Text>
                      </View>
                    </View>
                  </View>
                  {/*body*/}
                  <View className="relative p-6 flex-auto">
                    <View className="my-4 text-slate-500 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                      {arrayEditado.map((item) => (
                        <View key={item.id}>
                          <Text>{item.nombre} </Text>
                          <Text>{item.email} </Text>
                          <Text>+506 {item.telefono} </Text>
                          <Text>{item.direccion} </Text>
                          <Text>{item.fecha} </Text>
                          <View className="border font-bold grid grid-cols-3 text-center ">
                            <View className="border">
                              <Text>nombre: </Text>
                            </View>
                            <View className="border">
                              <Text>Cantidad: </Text>
                            </View>
                            <View className="border">
                              <Text>Precio Final</Text>
                            </View>
                          </View>
                          <View className="border font-bold grid grid-cols-3 text-center mt-5 mb-10 ">
                            <View className="">
                              <Text>{item.productos}</Text>
                            </View>
                            <View className="">
                              <Text>{item.cantidad}</Text>
                            </View>
                            <View className="">
                              <Text>{item.precio}</Text>
                            </View>
                          </View>
                          <View className="border font-bold grid grid-cols-2 text-center ">
                            <View className="border">
                              <View>
                                <Text> BN 100-01-050-000287-2 Colones (¢)</Text>
                                <Text> BCR 001-272476-6 Colones (¢)</Text>
                                <Text>
                                  {" "}
                                  IBAN BCR CR67015201001027247665 Colones (¢)
                                </Text>
                                <Text>
                                  BN IBAN CR17015105010010002870 Colones (¢)
                                </Text>
                              </View>
                            </View>
                            <View className="border">
                              <Text>{item.precio} </Text>
                              <Text>EXENTO: NO </Text>
                              <Text>IMPUESTO: {item.impuesto}%</Text>
                              <Text>
                                PRECIOfINAL :{" "}
                                {((Number(item.impuesto) / 100) *
                                  Number(item.precio) +
                                  Number(item.precio)) *
                                  Number(item.cantidad)}
                              </Text>
                            </View>
                          </View>
                        </View>
                      ))}
                      Especialistas en LLantas y baterias
                    </View>
                  </View>
                </View>
              </View>
            </View>
          </Page>
        </Document>
      ) : null}
    </>
  );
};

export default Pdf;
